---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="lastGLANCE"
  description="lastGLANCE is the next app from GLANCE Apps. Coming soon."
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="mb-10 font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-glance-muted transition-colors">GLANCE Apps</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-glance-muted">lastGLANCE</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim border border-glance-border-dim rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-glance-surface">
          Coming soon
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-none mb-6">
        <span class="text-glance-muted font-medium">last</span><span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="tracking-wider font-bold">GLANCE</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-glance-muted font-serif italic mb-10">
        Something new is coming.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
        <p>
          The next app in the GLANCE family is in development. Like everything
          we build, it will be calm, focused, and built with care.
        </p>
        <p>
          We'll share more when the time is right.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
          Stay in the loop
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted mb-4">
          To be notified when lastGLANCE launches, reach out and we'll add you
          to the list.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@glance-apps.com?subject=lastGLANCE%20interest"
          class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-accent link-underline"
        >
          Contact us to stay informed →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 section-rule">
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim">
          In the meantime, explore our existing apps:
          <a href="/apps/dayglance" class="text-glance-accent link-underline ml-1">dayGLANCE</a>
          <span class="mx-2 text-glance-border">·</span>
          <a href="/apps/lifeglance" class="text-glance-accent link-underline">lifeGLANCE</a>
          <span class="mx-2 text-glance-border">·</span>
          <a href="/apps/lastglance/downloads" class="text-glance-accent link-underline">Downloads (soon)</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
